55
00:03:56,190 --> 00:03:57,660
Thank you for your hard work today.

56
00:03:58,220 --> 00:03:59,320
We won't trouble you any further.

57
00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:00,840
Alright.

58
00:04:13,870 --> 00:04:15,070
Aren't you the one who...

59
00:04:15,080 --> 00:04:15,920
Goodbye.

60
