77
00:06:10,880 --> 00:06:12,360
Do you know?

78
00:06:12,360 --> 00:06:14,400
The first time Jiahao said
he wanted to marry you,

79
00:06:15,280 --> 00:06:16,480
he was only seven years old.

80
00:06:18,040 --> 00:06:21,240
He told me after he came back

81
00:06:21,680 --> 00:06:22,880
from your birthday party,

82
00:06:23,600 --> 00:06:24,440
"Mom,

83
00:06:25,110 --> 00:06:26,520
I want to marry Yue.

84
00:06:26,840 --> 00:06:28,500
I'll marry no one but her in this life."

85
00:06:29,940 --> 00:06:31,600
Isn't that funny?

86
00:06:32,640 --> 00:06:33,480
Drink.

87
00:06:37,080 --> 00:06:37,920
Drink.

88
00:06:45,320 --> 00:06:46,160
Yue,

89
00:06:47,950 --> 00:06:49,280
