93
00:06:59,440 --> 00:07:02,800
That is a blessing for a woman.

94
00:07:05,320 --> 00:07:07,120
Jiahao truly loves me sincerely.

95
00:07:08,080 --> 00:07:09,600
I have always known this.

96
00:07:13,860 --> 00:07:15,400
You and I are both women,

97
00:07:16,020 --> 00:07:17,080
so you will understand

98
00:07:17,920 --> 00:07:19,480
the painstaking efforts of a mom.

99
00:07:20,640 --> 00:07:22,720
As long as you and Jiahao are well,

100
00:07:24,480 --> 00:07:26,080
